00:21:11.355 --> 00:21:13.290
[ Upbeat music playing ]

515
00:21:13.324 --> 00:21:15.526
-Wow!
-Damn. son.

516
00:21:15.559 --> 00:21:17.228
That's clean.

517
00:21:17.261 --> 00:21:18.963
Our pool is amazing.
You're the best dad ever.

518
00:21:18.996 --> 00:21:22.099
Yeah. Who needs Boob World
when we got Dad's pool?

519
00:21:22.133 --> 00:21:24.001
I just want to make you all
happy.

520
00:21:24.034 --> 00:21:26.470
You did. Jerry.
You really did.

521
00:21:26.504 --> 00:21:28.272
Ah. yes!

522
00:21:28.305 --> 00:21:30.740
[ Laughter ]

523
00:21:30.773 --> 00:21:33.944
Oh. my God. I'm at a party.

524
00:21:36.413 --> 00:21:38.415
Pool season. baby!
Yeah!

525
00:21:38.449 --> 00:21:40.251
The Smith family has a pool!

526
00:21:40.284 --> 00:21:41.751
Man: ♪ One taste of you ♪

527
00:21:41.784 --> 00:21:46.423
♪ I knew I had
to have more ♪

528
00:21:46.457 --> 00:21:52.329
Woman: ♪ Your sweet taboo.
it brought me to my knees ♪

529
00:21:52.363 --> 00:21:59.303
Both: ♪ Oh. baby. now I'm lost
in your secret love ♪

530
00:21:59.336 --> 00:22:02.540
♪ You pulled me down ♪

531
00:22:02.573 --> 00:22:05.808
♪ Where no one can find us ♪

532
00:22:05.842 --> 00:22:09.846
♪ My lover in the darkest part
of night ♪

533
00:22:09.880 --> 00:22:13.850
♪ They'll never pull me
from your arms ♪

534
00:22:13.884 --> 00:22:17.154
Beth. we talked about this.

535
00:22:17.188 --> 00:22:19.190
Okay. I-I forgot.

536
00:22:21.358 --> 00:22:22.860
Thank you.

537
00:22:25.296 --> 00:22:26.463
It's not the same.

538
00:22:26.497 --> 00:22:28.199
Yeah. I know.

539
00:22:30.467 --> 00:22:31.902
Did you get any of that?
